Description: # Manual
        ```python
        from FadeMaxSize.findMax import find_max_file
        
        answer = find_max_file('path')
        print(answer)
        """
        {
            'file': 'path to largest file',
            'size': 1234 # Largest file size in kilobytes
        }
        """
        ```
        
        
